What you can do by emailing this contact
- Send any email to turn it into a new toast in your Inbox workspace.
- Use the subject "todo" to receive your current todo digest by email.

What you can do in replies
- Reply with "reword" to get an improved rewrite proposal.
- Reply with "transfer" to move the toast to the suggested workspace when Toastit can resolve one.
- Reply with both words to apply both actions in the same email.

Toastit is under heavy development. Suggestions, feedback, and help are very welcome at hello@toastit.cc.
